 the conventional Exclusive OR\nnetwork code and performs slightly better than the adaptive network coding\nscheme proposed by Koike-Akino et. al.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 14 Mar 2012 16:30:01 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 26 Mar 2012 18:55:23 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sat, 19 May 2012 07:10:23 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-04"}
