that a doubly block circulant Latin Square\nremoves this singularity. Simulation results are presented to show the\nsuperiority of QAM over PSK.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 15 Mar 2012 05:09:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2012-03-16"}
